        <div class="about-copy">
          <h1 class="about-title">About us</h1>
          <p>We believe flowers are not merely petals and stems — they are letters written by nature, waiting to be read by those who pause long enough to listen. Each bloom carries a story. Each color holds a memory.</p>
          <p>We gathered these stories in one place — not just to inform, but to remind. Because in a world that rushes, flowers still speak in silence. They speak of love that stays, grief that transforms, hope that returns with every spring. This website is our quiet offering. A garden of meanings. A place where you can find not only what a flower means, but what you yourself may have forgotten — that feelings have forms, that beauty has a language, and that even the smallest petal holds a universe within.</p>
          <p>We did not create this site to sell or impress. We created it to share what has always been true: flowers are the earth's way of telling us we are not alone. Let the flowers speak. And may you find exactly what your heart came looking for.</p>
          <p class="about-signature">— With roots reaching forward</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
